short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Save the prompt images and other information from the Midjourney / PromptHero web to your own Notion database

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This plugin is a part of "Prompt Visualizer" web tool, which use to save the prompt images and other information from the Midjourney / PromptHero web to your own Notion database
Guide：https://github.com/qiuzijian7/PromptVisualizerGuide
该插件是Prompt Visualizer工具的一部分，用于将Midjourney、PromptHero等网站上喜好的AI图像自动记录到Notion中，用于在PromptVisualizer网页工具上展示
教程：https://github.com/qiuzijian7/PromptVisualizerGuide
